query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS inspections (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  lead_id INT NOT NULL,
  key_tag_number VARCHAR(50),
  pre_scan_name1 VARCHAR(255),
  pre_scan_date1 TIMESTAMP NULL,
  pre_scan_name2 VARCHAR(255),
  pre_scan_date2 TIMESTAMP NULL,
  fill_tank ENUM('yes', 'no'),
  odometer_in VARCHAR(20),
  fuel_level_in VARCHAR(20),
  incentive_amount INT,
  incentive_name VARCHAR(255),
  incentive_paid_date TIMESTAMP NULL,
  incentive_check_number VARCHAR(100),
  referral_amount INT,
  referral_name VARCHAR(255),
  referral_paid_date TIMESTAMP NULL,
  referral_check_number VARCHAR(100),
  detail_by VARCHAR(255),
  detail_date TIMESTAMP NULL,
  jairo_qc VARCHAR(255),
  jairo_qc_date TIMESTAMP NULL,
  alec_kk VARCHAR(255),
  alec_kk_date TIMESTAMP NULL,
  specific_requests_checked VARCHAR(255),
  fueled_by VARCHAR(255),
  delivery_scheduled_by VARCHAR(255),
  delivery_date_time TIMESTAMP NULL,
  status ENUM('draft', 'pre_scan_complete', 'post_scan_complete', 'completed') DEFAULT 'draft',
  inspection_notes TEXT,
  incentive_notes TEXT,
  quote_request_notes TEXT,
  additional_notes TEXT,
  created_by VARCHAR(255),
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
